{"tid":1844123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫推求共識！！！]公投應否主動向藍絲釋出善意 connect哂所有人","createTime":"2020-01-26T13:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T14:31:07.000Z","uid":68667,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8de5a0c7728cac7792a6071cfc3f5092352ae0","tid":1844123,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲無疑係自私係咩都睇自己利益為先<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今時唔同往日</span></strong></span><br />\nWARS同封唔封關係會影響哂全部人不論你嘅政見<br />\n而大家都睇到藍絲今日粉嶺嘅表現<br />\n所以如果我地能夠 connect埋藍營<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意會真正轉哂過嚟我地依邊<br />\n勇武程度都可以再突破 甚至全民皆武<br />\n以後號召三罷/各樣活動都會更加凝聚到</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n但當然我地要做嘅就係放低過去嘅因怨 <br />\n同埋都要預咗教化藍絲所花嘅時間心力<br />\n<br />\n所以想係依到攞個共識:<br />\n正皮: we connect<br />\n負皮: 道不同不相為謀"},{"pid":"f995fbeb8c9727b3d195107ce3512179e1eb309e","tid":1844123,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"1.29 抗疫三罷 我地一齊罷！ 齊上齊落<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"695173db3dc6673c2035b085daec8efcceed2248","tid":1844123,"uid":188805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"團結次要敵人"},{"pid":"585471af2a857e9fc7ed088061b9615e2fa5df15","tid":1844123,"uid":68667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫推！！！光復香港睇今次！！！！！</span></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"86466cf9f0bf73114ee8d8e80aa39a16e9545514","tid":1844123,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"團結次要敵人"},{"pid":"d5803dca8b6d2e756ff4b487c525ecdc4d891e98","tid":1844123,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:2